room_title: Escape room "Saving Christmas" by Confundrum Escape Rooms in Idaho Falls
room_address: 763 S Woodruff Ave, Idaho Falls, ID 83404
room_description: Santa is preparing for the busiest night of the year and has discovered that he cannot find his hat or his most useful reindeer, Rudolph. Without his hat he would be violation of the Santa Clause uniform directive RH-01. The absense of Rudolph will put him at risk of being hoplessly lost in a blizzard, heavy fog or the smoke of the California fires. Please Save Christmas by helping Santa recover his hat that has been hidden by a mischevious elf and help recover Rudolph the Red Nosed Reindeer! Enjoy our Seasonal Christmas Escape Room and have a jolly holiday season.
